# Build-context hygiene: keep the image small and the build reproducible.
# The image is built from the lockfile + source only; everything installed or
# generated is recreated inside the build.

# Installed / generated
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/out

# VCS + CI + editor
.git
.gitignore
.github
.vscode
.idea

# Local env & secrets — runtime-injected on the VPS, never baked into the image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Supabase self-host stack & DB tooling — not needed to build the web app
supabase

# Docs & meta
**/*.md
LICENSE

# Test / coverage artifacts
**/coverage
**/.vitest
